ORLEANS HOUSE GALLERY AUTUMN TERM ART CLUBS
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Join an after school club... weekly after school clubs on Mondays,
    Wednesdays and Thursday for 5-15 year olds.

    Exciting weekly workshops offer budding young artists the
    opportunity to explore a broad range of artistic media and practice
    with our experienced gallery artists. Each term brings a varied
    selection of projects which are explored in group sizes of no more
    than sixteen, allowing participants to try more messy and
    adventurous media than may be possible at school.

